    "Pulse runs entirely on your Mac. It makes no outbound network calls (the only potential exception is the future update checker, which will be opt-in and point only at GitHub releases).": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse runs entirely on your Mac. It makes no outbound network calls (the only potential exception is the future update checker, which will be opt-in and point only at GitHub releases)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 完全运行在你的 Mac 本地，不会发起任何出站网络请求（未来若加入更新检查将是可选项，并且仅指向 GitHub Releases）。"
