    },
    "Checker mode — mostly quick dips today, not long-form focus.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Checker mode — mostly quick dips today, not long-form focus."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "检查员模式——今天基本是短停留，不是长段深度专注。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Welcome to Pulse": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Welcome to Pulse"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "欢迎使用 Pulse"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A local-first dashboard for the way you actually use your Mac. Pulse turns the noisy stream of clicks, key presses, scrolls and app switches into a daily story you can read in 30 seconds.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A local-first dashboard for the way you actually use your Mac. Pulse turns the noisy stream of clicks, key presses, scrolls and app switches into a daily story you can read in 30 seconds."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "本地优先的仪表盘，记录你真正使用 Mac 的方式。Pulse 把点击、按键、滚动、应用切换这些嘈杂的事件流，整理成 30 秒就能读完的每日故事。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Privacy promises": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Privacy promises"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "隐私承诺"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Before we ask for any permissions, here is what Pulse will and will not do — read it first.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Before we ask for any permissions, here is what Pulse will and will not do — read it first."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在请求任何权限之前，先把 Pulse 会做和不会做的事讲清楚——请先读完。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "All raw data stays inside ~/Library/Application Support/Pulse/. Nothing is ever uploaded.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All raw data stays inside ~/Library/Application Support/Pulse/. Nothing is ever uploaded."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "所有原始数据保留在 ~/Library/Application Support/Pulse/，永远不会上传。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No keystroke contents — only press counts. By default the key code is not stored either.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No keystroke contents — only press counts. By default the key code is not stored either."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "不记录按键内容——只记录按键次数。默认情况下连键码也不存。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No clipboard, no screen recording, no microphone, no camera, ever.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No clipboard, no screen recording, no microphone, no camera, ever."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "永远不读剪贴板、不录屏、不开麦克风、不开摄像头。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Window titles are SHA-256 hashed before being persisted.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Window titles are SHA-256 hashed before being persisted."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "窗口标题在落盘前会被 SHA-256 哈希。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pulse makes zero outbound network calls (a future opt-in update checker is the only exception, and it would only hit GitHub Releases).": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse makes zero outbound network calls (a future opt-in update checker is the only exception, and it would only hit GitHub Releases)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 不会发起任何出站网络请求（未来若加入更新检查也将是可选项，并且仅指向 GitHub Releases）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I've read these promises and want to continue.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I've read these promises and want to continue."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我已经读过这些承诺，希望继续。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grant Input Monitoring": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Grant Input Monitoring"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "授权 Input Monitoring"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grant Accessibility": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Grant Accessibility"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "授权 Accessibility"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grant permission": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Grant permission"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "授权"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pulse uses Input Monitoring to count clicks, key presses and scroll ticks system-wide. **It only counts events — it never records what you type.** macOS will quit and relaunch Pulse the moment you flip the switch; that's normal.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse uses Input Monitoring to count clicks, key presses and scroll ticks system-wide. **It only counts events — it never records what you type.** macOS will quit and relaunch Pulse the moment you flip the switch; that's normal."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 使用 Input Monitoring 在系统层面统计点击、按键、滚动次数。**只数事件本身，绝不记录你打了什么。** 你勾选这个开关时 macOS 会立即退出并重启 Pulse，这是正常现象。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pulse uses Accessibility to read which app is in the foreground and (optionally) the title of the active window. Window titles are hashed before being stored.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse uses Accessibility to read which app is in the foreground and (optionally) the title of the active window. Window titles are hashed before being stored."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 使用 Accessibility 来识别当前前台应用，以及（可选地）当前活跃窗口的标题。窗口标题会先被哈希再落盘。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This permission is required for Pulse to function.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This permission is required for Pulse to function."
          }
